          <div class="words">
            
              <p>Autarky not Oligarchy</p>
<p>We should all be heading to self sufficiency locally. regionally, inside the state and within the country.
with most needs met locally and fewer goods brought from outside the immediate area.
A community can supply its own needs and provide the labor need to do that along with adjusting wages to fairly distribute wealth gained.</p>
<p>To hell with the bankers empire and inefficient use of local labor and renewable resources.
The IMF, WTO, World Bank and transnational corporates all bleed local resources and wealth.</p>
<p><a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.zerohedge.com/news/2014-01-16/what-if-nations-were-less-dependent-one-another">http://www.zerohedge.com/news/2014-01-16/what-if-nations-were-less-dependent-one-another</a></p>
            
          </div>
